0.01 Sat 16 April 2005
----------------------

  * (16 Apr 2005) added a Get Info button
  	The Get Info button will populate the form with the Info
  from the selected file-with-a-similar-name in the same directory
  as the current file.  Useful for multi-part stories whose info
  is the same except for the part-number.

  * (16 Apr 2005) initial checkin
